snippet.title: Ostranauts Teaser
snippet.description:
Ostranauts is a noir spaceship-life simulator set in the NEO Scavenger universe.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1022980

Website: https://bluebottlegames.com/games/ostranauts
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ostranauts
Discord:https://discord.gg/jgJu3GDreW

Music by Josh Culler, a.k.a. Invisible Acropolis: https://soundcloud.com/invisible-acropolis
Trailer by M Joshua Cauller: http://mjoshua.com
Audio by James Marantette: https://soundcloud.com/james-marantette
